summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 8860, entitled "An Ordinance licensing and regulating theatres, concert halls and other public amusements of like character in the City of Seattle and providing a penalty for the violation thereof and repealing Ordinance No. 7729, approved February 7th, 1902 and Ordinance No. 8030, approved April 28th, 1902" approved November 18, 1902 and Ordinance No. 11432, approved November 2, 1904, amendatory thereof.
